defaultRepresenting the nations, regions, communities
default1.10.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultPact will continue to the monitor the BBC’s progress towards the target of realising 50% of network television by spend, outside London, by 2016. This target, set by the BBC Trust, includes 17% to be spent in Scotland, Wales and Northern Ireland respective
defaultly. We are pleased to see that the BBC is on schedule to achieve this with 46% of spend achieved out of London and just under 16% in the devolved countries. The progress made on out of London spend will help contribute towards the sustained and organic gro
defaultwth of the sector across the UK.
